    public class BadFusion
extends BadHydraNode<java.lang.String,java.lang.String,java.lang.String,Fusion>
implements Fusion, StdJSONFeatures
    An implementation of Fusion that always fails. Primary use is where a non-null Fusion lightweight object is needed but doesn't implement any functionality.

        public void freeze()
        Description copied from interface: Fusion
        A programmer directed promise that no further modifications will be made to this object. The implementation is encouraged but not required to detect any further modifications. In the event that a broken promise is detected, the effect will be a thrown UnsupportedOperationException.
